phrases: Gohan- chan, you are going to catch up with everythin' that you have fallen behind on.
All we are doing is changing his bandages.
What a loud patient this is.
On second thought, I should not be here.
We have to find that Saiyan spaceship quickly.
You need to hurry and recover from your injuries.
We never know when that Saiyan is going to attack again.
You need to completely recover before that happens.
Gohan- chan is not having anythin' to do with that anymore!
I am not lettin' him get into any more dangerous situations like that again!
M- my injuries are not all that serious, so...
You have got to get treated properly, or you are not going to get any better!
They said that after Gohan and I spend three days in the hospital, we will be fine.
They said it would be four months before my injuries heal.
They also said I might not be back to my former self.
In another month, I will have some new Senzu beans.
You know, you look just like a mummy in there.
I went through all that nastiness, and they are not even going to keep me here.
You are just after the hospital's food, are not you?
When Yajirobe thought he was going to be done in by that Saiyan,
I got lotsa respect for ya!
I was just sayin' that to get him off his guard!
Well, in any case, you all really done well!
And everyone who is dead is comin' back to life, too.
Mm-hmm, that is, if we can get to Planet Namek.
It will be all right, that is for sure!
I thought you were some weird nurse.
According to those who found it, this object,
which was discovered in the devastation of Metro East,
appears to be a vehicle that came from space, though that cannot be determined.
Apparently, when this object was found, there were two of them,
but soon after, one of them suddenly flew away from the scene.
Those scientists have already carried it away.
Let us use the remote control that Kuririn brought back, and call it here!
That will surprise them, I am sure.
Are you sure that is going to work?
I thoroughly checked it out last night.
It is nice that we can watch it right here on TV, huh?
It is going to start moving...
W - what in the world could have happened here!?
There is wreckage from the object all over!
Could that have been the self-destruct switch?
Without that spaceship, we cannot go to Planet Namek!
I probably could not get there using Kinto Un, either.
This is your fault for picking up strange remote controls!
Bulma- san, you are the one who was hasty to push those switches.
You really have one, Popo- san?
He stays at Kami- sama's place.
But he is been there at Kami's palace
since long before this current Kami- sama was ever there.
Say, what do you mean, probably ?
Someone come with me to check.
nobody else would know if it is a spaceship.
I mean, does not that man have a dangerous look in his eye?
Bulma, what is taking you so long?
We are counting on you, Bulma!
I am not like those guys.
H- how did he do that just now?
Still, what kind of spaceship is it?
That is the ends of the earth, you know!
You mean, we came this far in that one instant?
Say, do you mean there is something like a spaceship here?
Hey, are you listening to me?
You have not brought me here to this far-flung place...
I- I will have to examine it...
Hang on, what is going on?
Tell me what this is, exactly!
About 100 years ago, Kami- sama told Mister Popo of old times.
Kami- sama said lived here in Yunzabit when child.
People not live there, so why you there?
I do not know why I was there.
I must have hit my head,
and lost all of my memories up to that point.
All I had was a letter that said they would be coming later.
I do not see where this story is going.
Kami- sama as child waited long time for parents.
Not knew what happened, but waited.
I had my house there in Yunzabit, after all.
I trusted that my parents would surely return there.
However, no matter how long I waited, nobody ever came.
There was hardly anything there to eat, either.
How long did I wait there?
No, it must have been 30 years.
Finally, I gave up, and, leaving my house behind, I left Yunzabit.
Once in a while, I went back to see how it was doing, but there was never any change.
So, what does that have to do with this?
But you know, thinking back on it now, it was a strange house.
I did not realize it until I had learned more about the world,
but that house was really quite unusual.
It was round, with four legs, and looked almost like an insect.
Its door did not have any knobs or locks, but would open when a word was spoken to it.
This not house, but rather, spaceship?
That Kaio person said that long ago,
Planet Namek went through some abnormal weather, and they nearly died out.
Mister Popo also heard Kaio- sama's voice speaking.
Then remembered story of this house.
Thought what if, came here searching, and this here.
If this really is a spaceship, then your story earlier would indeed be consistent.
When Planet Namek had bad time,
Kami- sama's parents put child Kami- sama aboard, sent to Earth.
His parents meant to escape afterward, when they were able to,
but there was some kind of accident...
which is to say, they died...
After all, no matter how you look at this thing, it does not seem like a house.
This has to be a spaceship!
But even if that is so, can we use it or not?
The door moved, so it has to have power, right?
I wonder if there is a code number or something.
If it worked as easily as that,
then when Kami- sama was a child, he would have tried pushing them, too.
It looks like this thing does not work using switches.
I wonder if Bulma- san will really find anything for us.
All we can do now is pray.
We are counting on you, Bulma.
Could it be some kind of sensor?
After all, that is the password you use for going in and out.
After all, back at that Tenkaichi Tournament,
Kami- sama and Piccolo spoke in that strange language.
That must be the Namekian language.
Supposing that Namekian language, Mister Popo knows those words.
Piccolo means other world in those words.
Why did not you say so sooner?
Piccolo Daimao means the Demon King of Another World.
I know, how about around Jupiter for now?
Does not this spaceship have any safety belts!?
Just now, you said want to go toilet in Namekian.
We have to be careful what we say!
We did it, we did it!
Now Kami- sama come back to life.
Now all that remains is a departure for Planet Namek.
